**Steps to deploy Docker Stack**

**Deploy stack**  
 docker stack deploy -c docker-compose.yml teststack1  
**Remove stack**  
docker stack rm teststack1  
**Path for volumes(data)**  
 cd /var/lib/docker/volumes/teststack1_prometheus_data/  
 **To see all running services**  
 docker service ls  
 **Reload Prometheus without restart**  
 curl -X POST http://<yourip>:9090/-/reload